-- European Fiscal Compact Is ‘Important,’ ECB’s Asmussen Says
-- B y   O l i v e r   S u e s s
-- 2012-02-05T17:06:39Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-05/european-fiscal-compact-is-important-ecb-s-asmussen-says.html
European Central Bank Executive Board
member Joerg Asmussen said  Europe ’s fiscal compact is important
to strengthen rules, he wrote in a guest commentary in German
newspaper  Handelsblatt .  “It is the right medicine for what we found to be the
major cause of the debt crisis, the lack of budgetary
discipline,” Asmussen wrote, according to the newspaper.  To contact the reporter on this story:
